title: What We Learned From Week 8 in the N.F.L.
description: A.J. Brown and the Eagles’ personnel make play-calling simple, Derrick Henry is back, and the Vikings’ success depends on football no-brainers: win the turnover battle and don’t commit penalties.
dc:creator: Derrik Klassen
media:description: A.J. Brown caught three touchdown passes from Jalen Hurts in the first half of the Eagles’ 35-13 win over the Steelers.
